These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, photography
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, musician
1. the doctor is in an even position##4
2. the musician is the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | photography | baking |
| Job     | musician    | doctor   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, water
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, cycling
1. the person who's sport is parkour is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | water | tea        |
| Sport      | parkour  | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, trance
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, american
1. the colombian is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | folk |
| Nationality   | colombian | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, coffee
There 2 different types of food: lime, apple
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person eating apple is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | tea      | coffee |
| Food       | lime | apple    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
