The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, rowing
1. the australian is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the japanese##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Nationality   | australian | japanese   |
| Sport         | lacrosse | rowing |

